# AssetCore backoffice — AssetCore's internal client-instance console.
# Defaults to same-origin /api (apps/api's /api/admin/* routes) — no vars are
# required for local dev (Vite proxies /api, see vite.config.js) or for a
# same-origin production deploy (nginx proxies /api and serves this SPA at
# /admin/ — see deploy/nginx/nginx.conf). Only set VITE_API_URL for a
# split-host setup where the API lives elsewhere.
VITE_API_URL=
